; Coverage for xact.cc (balance.is_long with null post)
; (virtual_balance.is_long with virtual null post)
; When amounts are pure integers (no commodity), balance is stored as
; a long integer value; this tests that the null post fill-in handles it.

2024/01/01 Integer amounts
    Expenses:Food    5
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Virtual integers
    Expenses:Rent     $10.00
    Assets:Cash      $-10.00
    [Budget:Rent]     3
    [Budget:Reserve]

test reg
24-Jan-01 Integer amounts       Expenses:Food                     5            5
                                Assets:Cash                      -5            0
24-Jan-02 Virtual integers      Expenses:Rent                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
                                [Budget:Rent]                     3            3
                                [Budget:Reserve]                 -3            0
end test
